`paranoid: true` preserved. Sequelize `alter: true` in `server/index.js` auto-migrates on startup.

**`server/routes/incident.js`** — Final state after all changes:
```js
const { verifyToken } = require('../middlewares/auth');
const ALLOWED_STATUSES = ['Active', 'Investigating', 'Escalated to Security', 'Cleared'];

// POST / — manual FM creation (verifyToken)
router.post("/", verifyToken, async (req, res) => { ... resolutionStatus: 'Active' hardcoded });

