5. Problem Solving:
- **Seed-on-first-load vs live seeding**: User said not to implement AI-triggered seeding but wanted static data to persist. Solution: one-time sequential POST of 12 static incidents on first component mount, gated by `localStorage` flag. Sequential (not parallel) to avoid hammering the server.
